# MatBuilder v0.1.0

Material Structure Modeling Toolkit — 交互式晶体结构建模工具包

## Quick Start

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
mkdir structs && cp your_structure.vasp structs/PCM.vasp
python run.py


MatBuilder/
